  "body": "<html><body><div class=\"field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item\" property=\"schema:text\"><p> </p><p>Insurers and intermediaries know that innovation has the potential to disrupt their current business and operating models. And they know that they need to innovate faster than their competitors to defend and grow their business. Yet few have found a ‘winning formula’ for embedding innovation into their people, products or processes.</p><p><a href=\"https://internationalinsurance.org/sites/default/files/2018-01/KPMG%20Frontiers%20-%20insurance%20innovation.pdf\"><strong>read more &gt;</strong></a></p></div></body></html>",
